com.samsung.android.sdk.composer.document

Class SpenContentWeb

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.sdk.composer.document.SpenContentBase
      • com.samsung.android.sdk.composer.document.SpenContentWeb

  • public class SpenContentWeb
extends SpenContentBase
    SpenContentWeb Class.
    ContentWeb has the basic content properties by inherit the SpenContentBase,
    and has additional functions for web page contents.
    Some APIs and variables are moved or integrated to super class SpenContentBase since 5.0.0.
    Since:
    5.0.0
